<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Permaweb Dropper
    script(src="scripts/app.ts")
  body
    .container
      h1 Permaweb Dropper
      p Save your files forever on the 
        a(href="https://arweave.org", target="_blank") permaweb
        | . 
        br
        | You need to login with your Arweave wallet, don't have one? 
        a(href="https://www.arweave.org/wallet", target="_blank") Grab yours here.

      .dropzone
        input#browse(type="file", name="browse" multiple)
        img#pass(src="images/pass.png", alt="Arweave Wallet")
        img#water(src="images/water.png", alt="DropZone", style="display: none")
        h2 Drag and drop your Arweave wallet
        h3 or
        a(href="#").browse Browse for wallet

    .container
      .tags
        p You can add custom tags to your uploaded files. 
          br
          | All files deployed will have these tags.

        table(style="display: none")
          thead
            tr
              th Tag Name
              th Tag Value
          tbody
            tr
              td
                input.tagName(type="text")
              td
                input.tagValue(type="text")
          
        a.addTag(href="#") Add Tag

      

    .container.files-container

    footer
